een conducted; the initial stages of the investigation have been successfully completed bar the identification of the bodies, which is scheduled for later this morning; then the second stage of the investigation will begin \x{2013}I swallow\x{2026}\x{2018}All reports must be completed and submitted to Headquarters this morning,\x{2019} Adachi is now telling the First Team, the Second Team and the uniforms from the Atago, Meguro and Mita police stations. \x{2018}Following the completion of the identification process, there will be a second meeting later today at <<4 p.m.|5>>\x{2019}\x{2018}Attention!\x{2019} shouts one of the sergeants \x{2013}\x{2018}Bow!\x{2019} the sergeant shouts \x{2013}\x{2018}Dismissed!\x{2019}I run back to the toilets. I vomit again. Brown bile. I walk over to the sink. I spit. I wipe my mouth. I turn on a tap. I wash my face. I look up into the mirror. I stare into the mirror \x{2013}No one is who they say they are \x{2026}In the upstairs corridor I wait for Nishi and Kimura. I take them to one side. I ask them, \x{2018}Have you written up your reports?\x{2019}They both nod. They both say, \x{2018}Yes, we have.\x{2019}\x{2018}Then I want you to go to Toshima Ward,\x{2019} I tell them. \x{2018}I want you to go to the ward office. I want you to ask again about this Takahashi of Z\x{14d}shigaya, Toshima\x{2026}\x{2019}Kimura nods again but Nishi says, \x{2018}The First Team have already been up there.\x{2019}\x{2018}I know that,\x{2019} I tell him. \x{2018}And I know they couldn\x{2019}t find him or any mention of him, but his name on a statement of employment in his bag in that park is the only name we have found so far and, remember, our body is only bones and those bones need a name or they\x{2019}ll always be bones\x{2026}\x{2019}Nishi nods. Kimura nods. They both bow. They both turn to leave. I wait until they\x{2019}ve gone and then I run. I run back to the toilets to vomit a third time. Yellow bile. I turn on the tap. I wash my face. I l